<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10272326>
    dc:description "Figs 15–20. Geocorine true bugs of the Malagasy region (dorsal habitus): 15 = Geocoris pallidipennis mauritii Stål, 1854 (male, MNHN); 16 = Germalus banari Kondorosy et Kóbor, 2016 (paratype, male, MNHN); 17 = Germalus benyovszkyi Kondorosy et Kóbor, 2016 (holotype, male, MNHN); 18 = Germalus kinbergi Stål, 1860 (lectotype, female, NHRS); 19 = Hypogeocoris alluaudi (Montandon, 1908) (male, MNHN); 20 = Hypogeocoris violaceus (Signoret, 1881)" ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10272326/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10272324>
    dc:description "Figs 12–14. Lectotype (present designation) of Geocoris (Piocoris) junodi Montandon, 1907:" ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10272324/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

